Provider Endpoint

Source: R/S7_pro.R
pro.Rd

Provider Endpoint

Provider Endpoint Group

Usage

proMain(alias)

proGroup(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> title alias

Value

An S7 <proMain> object.

An S7 <proGroup> object.

Examples
